This is a superfast mp3 download client for amazon mp3. 
it is under active development now. 

Available features:
1) supports retry and resume
2) supports parallel downloads using the superfast pycurl library

How to install:
pycrypto and pycurl are the prerequsites of this tool. You can install both of these packages using pip or easy_install. 

pip install pycrypto
pip install pycurl

or 

easy_install pycrypto
easy_install pycrypto


Rest everything should work right out of the box. :) 
